items.title: LinkedIn Content Automation
items.description: Automated LinkedIn content generation pipeline. Fetches news from RSS feeds, filters for relevance, generates high-signal posts using AI, and manages an approval workflow via Telegram before posting.

items.title: Community Messages
items.description: Crypto community engagement bot. Monitors multiple crypto news sources, filters for high-impact updates, and broadcasts summaries to Telegram communities. Includes rate limiting and duplicate detection.

items.title: X Content Automation - Crypto
items.description: High-frequency X (Twitter) bot for crypto analysis. Ingests market news, uses AI to identify key narratives, and generates sharp, high-signal tweets. Features memory buffers to avoid repetition.

items.title: AI Facebook Ad Spy Tool
items.description: Automated Facebook Ad Library scraper and analyzer. Fetches competitor ads, downloads media, uses Gemini 1.5 Pro to analyze visuals and video content, and saves structured insights to Google Sheets.

items.title: Email Inbox Manager
items.description: Intelligent email classification and drafting system. Categorizes incoming Gmail messages (Internal, Support, Promotions), uses OpenAI to draft context-aware responses, and notifies Slack for high-priority items.

items.title: Firecrawl Search
items.description: Advanced web search agent using Firecrawl. Converts natural language queries into complex search operators, scrapes full-page content, and returns structured markdown results for research or monitoring.

items.title: HeyGen Avatar
items.description: Automated video generation pipeline. Scrapes news content, generates a concise script using AI, and produces a professional avatar video using HeyGen's API.

items.title: LinkedIn Comment Scraper
items.description: Viral post lead generation system. Scrapes LinkedIn comments, enriches profiles with company data, qualifies leads based on industry/size, and drafts personalized DM outreach scripts.

items.title: Live Search Grok API
items.description: Real-time X (Twitter) intelligence agent. Uses Grok API to monitor tech leaders, breaking news, and viral trends, providing balanced summaries and citations from live social data.

items.title: Pre-meeting Prep - Calendly
items.description: Automated meeting preparation agent. Triggers on Calendly bookings, researches attendees and companies using Perplexity AI, analyzes meeting goals, and emails a comprehensive briefing with an audio summary.

items.title: Ultimate Browser Agent
items.description: Comprehensive browser automation suite for ad intelligence. An advanced version of the Ad Spy tool with enhanced error handling, multi-format media processing, and deeper analysis capabilities.

items.title: iMessage Automation
items.description: SMS/iMessage automation bridge. Receives messages via webhook, uses an AI agent with memory to generate context-aware replies, and sends responses back via Twilio.
